Film.Synopsis: A talented young getaway driver - inspired by his own personal soundtrack - meets the girl of his dreams, but is caught up in a doomed heist. Crime action.
Former villain-turned-agent Gru takes on 80s-obsessed super-villain Balthazar Bratt - and faces a showdown with his own brother, Dru. Animated comedy with Steve Carell.
When Emily is dumped just before an exotic vacation to South America, she decides to take her ultra-cautious mother instead. Comedy with Amy Schumer and Goldie Hawn.
After his debut in Captain America: Civil War, young Peter Parker navigates between life at school and as a web-slinging superhero. Superhero action in the Marvel universe.
When middle-aged couple Scott and Kate Johansen are unable to pay their daughter's college bills, they decide to open an illegal casino in their basement. Comedy with Will Ferrell and Amy Poehler.
